org.openintents.tools.simulator.model.telnet

类 TelnetSimulatorModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openintents.tools.simulator.model.telnet.TelnetSimulatorModel

  • public class TelnetSimulatorModel
extends java.lang.Object
    TelnetSimulatorModel keeps the data (the model behind the GUI) of the TelnetSimulator (listeners, etc.) TelnetSimulator simulates, using a telnet communication with the emulator, the battery level and the gps position.

    ilarele
